{"tid":537772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"浸大生反普通話試　《環時》評論批水平差　指學校須認清「港獨」歪風嚴懲","createTime":"2018-01-23T04:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T05:06:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e8d6acf0df53ca59120e1c4e8f47c9be92cde820","tid":537772,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:14:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180123/s00001/4810428ae4868b2480949fdfe17c8181.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180123%2Fs00001%2F4810428ae4868b2480949fdfe17c8181.jpg&h=22a9397d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n浸會大學學生上周三（17日）到語文中心，抗議學校普通話豁免試評分機制欠透明及不能重考等，引起關注。內地官媒《環球時報》刊載自稱浸大舊生的香港學研社研究員傅霾澈評論，批評學生普通話水平太差，又說反普通話本質是「去中國化」，學校需要認清事件嚴重性，懲處不可「輕輕放下」。<br />\n<br />\n文章題為＜普通話也有「原罪」？＞，指中國發展一日千里，普通話日益受到世界重視，浸大將普通話能力列為畢業要求之一，符合世界潮流，也是為學生前途着想。<br />\n<br />\n文章稱，今次豁免試試卷不難，及格率卻只有三成，「只能說明一些學生的普通話水平太差」，認為這次浸大學生會反對普通話豁免試本質，是「去中國化」，通過語言差異製造與內地割裂。<br />\n<br />\n文章表示，去年9月開學時，香港的大學出現「港獨」歪風，而這股歪風根源仍在，只要一有適當條件就會重新冒出，故學校須認清事件嚴重性，「如果懲處上僅是『高高舉起、輕輕放下』，只會對其他大學的學生產生 『縱容就是鼓勵』的作用」。<br />\n<br />\n文章重申，中國在國際上影響力與日俱增，全球各地都興起學普通話熱潮，「如果香港的一些年輕人一定要逆世界發展大勢而行，相信他們的競爭對手只會拍手稱快」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180123/s00001/1516671753264\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180123%2Fs00001%2F1516671753264&d=dKoicb9uGzfvckZArvOw0U%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=a7b82cbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180123%2Fs00001%2F1516671753264&h=ea694bac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180123/s00001/1516671753264</a>"},{"pid":"3455cdc48866dede01fa87a94bc4aef54f8e1512","tid":537772,"uid":36901,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:16:53.000Z","msg":"乜撚都港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c3ddf2164845c7ff0d83b229e9032eaa64a124","tid":537772,"uid":47359,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:18:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原來拒學普通話就係支持港獨<br />\n環時都知身有屎鬼拍後尾枕講出推廣普通話係政治任務嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班港豬藍絲重focus喺粗口道 </span>"},{"pid":"eb7327b5da7ae5df2430ee60b9a8379ca3957e70","tid":537772,"uid":11001,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3455cdc48866dede01fa87a94bc4aef54f8e1512","tid":537772,"uid":36901,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:16:53.000Z","msg":"乜撚都港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:20:37.000Z","msg":"咁唔滿意咪踢走香港，再唔係咪出兵鎮壓囉，一日到黑淨係識大隻講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a20995b33ef29809252fde17e3f5fbf260487a","tid":537772,"uid":89530,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:22:06.000Z","msg":"乜都瀨上港獨，人哋唔係反普通話試，係反個評分標準，都唔知係邊個想分化兩地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"289e562907156e9f36c186527ac33a3f3de53d7c","tid":537772,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5fd850fe5503d1d69c36f8454d2781d8e838b0a","tid":537772,"uid":86841,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:23:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd38181d2058b0eb5aca9c605906515ae9019191","tid":537772,"uid":4964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:26:28.000Z","msg":"將黑既改成白，白既改成黑，原告改為被告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f21151f7e439bca1e12b8ca3ead9e5606821f7a","tid":537772,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime